              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The copper foils, 0.1 and 0.05 mm thick,",
                "the aluminium disks, 1.2 and 3. mm thick, had a",
                "diameter of a 33 mm.",
                "Accurate thicknesses were obtained by weighing these",
